title: Medford MA, 3 BED / 2 BATH w/master suite on third floor!
posting_body: ['Available Sept 1st', '3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom unit in Medford.', 'Lots of space, eat-in kitchen, and third floor bonus room!', 'Great location that allows quick access to many types of transportation.', 'Quick walk to Medford Square restaurants and shops.', 'Perfect location to take advantage of a short T ride or Uber to downtown Boston and surrounding areas!', 'Additional Details:', 'Fee: no fee', 'Features: Eat in Kitchen.', 'Separate dining room.', 'Appliances include: Refrigerator, Stove, Dishwasher, Microwave, Disposal.', 'Front and back porches, 2 floors of space.', 'Hardwood floors.', '2 queen-sized bedrooms on 2nd-floor, huge master suite on 3rd floor with bathroom and bonus space.', 'Location: Medford/Medford Square', 'Bath: 2', 'Bedrooms: 3', 'Available: September 1st, 2022', 'Additional details:', 'Two-Family house - unit is located on the 2nd & 3rd floor', 'Close to 93 and other major routes, short walk to bus, short drive to both Orange and Commuter lines', 'Walking distance to Medford square restaurants and shopping', 'Easy and plentiful on street parking', 'Additional off-street driveway parking is negotiable ($50/month/spot)', 'Washer/Dryer hookups, Cable Ready.', 'Utilities not included.', 'Pricing & availability subject to change.']
